{"tid":844663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 九龍灣商廈翻新車場　工人疑觸電死亡","createTime":"2018-10-02T04:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T05:52:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1161f2bfed962494ea6f38b6480c8675fc73645e","tid":844663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"今日(2日)早上10時20分，九龍灣啓祥道22號一商廈的停車場，一名年約40歲工人，在上址工作期間懷疑觸電昏迷，工友發現大驚報警。工人由救護車送院搶救，送院時面色紫黑已無反應，惜終告不治。警方正在場調查意外原因。多名親友接到通知趕抵醫院，其中事主母親驚聞噩耗後，坐於輪椅上掩面痛哭，需由親友安撫。據悉，事發時工人正開動一把風扇。<br />\n<br />\n現場商廈停車場由6月開始進行翻新工程，車場內一處闢作臨時工作間，門口有木板圍封，場內地面放有牛角風扇、拖板及裝修工具。今晨負責人返回上址時，發現一名工人昏迷倒地，面部及身體發黑，揭發事件。警方正調查工人是否觸電導致昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181002/bkn-20181002103922576-1002_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181002%2Fbkn-20181002103922576-1002_00822_001.html&d=XVj5jUj6%2FfVLMFfG0wJq7BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=47054ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181002/bkn-20181002103922576-1002_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5db85e854baed37274369f1ec3dffb39b5c19f28","tid":844663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"面部及身體發黑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0f7669e50c244cd892ada5fed7fceea4999a29","tid":844663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181002/photo/bkn-20181002103922576-1002_00822_001_02b.jpg?20181002122607\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181002%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181002103922576-1002_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20181002122607&h=42ff1337&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f17cbfa9c8ee8fffa4a0c88243b9eae8b26f4fc","tid":844663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:59:56.000Z","msg":"返工 返到變成酷刑拷問咁死法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9dfd01238d99d68da2df5a6ecfaa7b398febc4","tid":844663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}